    "created_at": "2016-04-07T11:17:15Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-04-07T11:17:15Z",
    "body": "The `printToPDF` API sends messages to the renderer process, while the renderer process is still waiting for the main process to respond the previous message, so this results in a dead lock. I'm afraid this can not be fixed because of the natural of `ipc.sendSync`, I'll update the docs for this.\n"
